From: appkins <13772502+appkins@users.noreply.github.com>
Date: Mon, 16 Mar 2026 13:02:42 -0500
Subject: [PATCH 07/15] mfd: add RP1 multi-function device driver

Add MFD driver for the RP1 chip, a PCIe-attached device on
Raspberry Pi 5 that provides GPIO, Ethernet, USB, and other
peripherals through its child devices.

Link: https://github.com/sidero-community/u-boot
Signed-off-by: appkins <13772502+appkins@users.noreply.github.com>
---
